The “number” of Ukrainian refugees during the past month (now) surpasses the next highest number of refugees from Venezuela. The total “count” is growing. However, are the proportions or “rates” of refugees from the other countries higher than Ukraine’s based on their respective total populations?

@Guilherme S. 
